      <del rend="strikethrough">my friends</del></line>
    <line>the superior advantages of m<retrace hand="#pbs" cause="clarify">y</retrace>
      friends.</line>
    <line>The <del rend="strikethrough">Father</del> old man, I could percieve,</line>
    <line>often endeavoured to encourage his</line>
