    <line>he called them. <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">to cast off their melancholy.</add>
      </mod> He would talk in</line>
    <line>a cheerful accent with an <mod>
