    <line>ly found that her manners and tone</line>
    <line>were more cheerful after having listen</line>
    <line>end to <del rend="strikethrough">the</del> the exhortations of her father</line>
    <line>It was not thus with Felix. He was</line>
    <line>always the saddest of the groupe And</line>
    <line>even to my unpractised senses he</line>
